{"tid":618683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 用完即棄！逾千中人壽保險經紀突被解約追獎金","createTime":"2018-04-06T04:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T14:11:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9962fa593b4dc42c559d02c5a045b325b3c73cf8","tid":618683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"保險業界與代理人之間的「魔鬼合約」已非新鮮事。新入行的保險經紀，不少雖享有公司提供的津貼，一旦「被炒」，所謂津貼立即call back（收回）。不過，早前中人壽大批「裁員」，據了解，一千多名保險代理人於合約期滿前被終止合約，並「按合約」向他們討回已付的津貼及奬金，涉款最少逾350萬元。工會質疑中人壽「用完即棄」，蓄意解約以剝削大批代理人的準貼及獎金。中人壽回覆指，公司已展開內部調查，暫不會回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「做得多賠得多」</span><br />\n<br />\n職工盟近日收到超過60個投訴，苦主被追討的金額由數千至10多萬元不等，共涉及金額約350萬元。苦主以中年婦女及新移民為主，她們於2016年成為保險代理，大部分簽了兩年合約，有些簽約後沒有售出任何產品，被追討數千元培訓費；有些當成正職，一年多以來簽了廿幾張單，卻「做得多賠得多」，慘被追討十多萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大量招<span style=\"color: red;\">聘新移民</span>　做夠單後「一腳踢開」<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n她又嘆，因事件常跟丈夫爭吵，近日開始被追數公司追討欠款，目前亦僅以兼職維持生活，壓力倍增：「無覺好瞓，唔知點算好。」她認為，公司刻意大量招聘新移民：「覺得佢哋親戚朋友的單做到差唔多，就一腳踢開。」她又指，她所屬的分區原本有約70至80人，不過近日已被裁剩約20多人：「餘下的人大部分已經滿了約，公司炒咗佢哋都無著數。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175089/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%80%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A7%A3%E7%B4%84%E8%BF%BD%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%A3%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F175089%2F%25E9%25AD%2594%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B4%2580%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%258D%258E%25E9%2587%2591-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%25A3%2584&d=xEl4g9mVlcyy5DgLu6EKaZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a84fce49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175089/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%80%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A7%A3%E7%B4%84%E8%BF%BD%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%A3%84</a>"},{"pid":"bd54b07b3065810fbee90e2f85a8266c1dbd4a73","tid":618683,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"大量招聘新移民　做夠單後「一腳踢開」<br />\n大量招聘新移民　做夠單後「一腳踢開」<br />\n大量招聘新移民　做夠單後「一腳踢開」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce06fb086ec6deb1bdc94bde4f86cab38bce319","tid":618683,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1334820/org/729c6c138e2011fbaeeb69c85221a761.JPG/9I-nvweYlzDbHot_uK60PGZv1hyofhDYXmiuRF5orkQ?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1334820%2Forg%2F729c6c138e2011fbaeeb69c85221a761.JPG%2F9I-nvweYlzDbHot_uK60PGZv1hyofhDYXmiuRF5orkQ%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=d7dcdb11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dce4eaddc07beee9cd12c46b49619cfaa3452e8","tid":618683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"保險IT化"},{"pid":"94199ba1d1043a97d05175f812e480322f9e218d","tid":618683,"uid":12021,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b56ecb9049185d84cbe681d2b14c90300967ad7d","tid":618683,"uid":137921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201