多人：「餘下的人大部分已經滿了約，公司炒咗佢哋都無著數。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175089/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%80%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A7%A3%E7%B4%84%E8%BF%BD%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%A3%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F175089%2F%25E9%25AD%2594%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B4%2580%25E7%25AA%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%258D%258E%25E9%2587%2591-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%25A3%2584&d=xEl4g9mVlcyy5DgLu6EKaZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a84fce49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/175089/%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E7%B6%93%E7%B4%80%E7%AA%81%E8%A2%AB%E8%A7%A3%E7%B4%84%E8%BF%BD%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%A3%84</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"綜援必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"c372d53147c501afcbecdc2e03d2b478554722b8","tid":618683,"uid":95520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<br />\n保險狗呢啲無學歷無經驗無智商嘅工請人有幾難<br />\n炒完你地容乜易請番批新<br />\n唔係你地以為自己著西裝番工就專業人士"},{"pid":"f89c0cde8a05a2f8187e7f2649ddc75864efbb20","tid":618683,"uid":51200,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"之前去英國保誠個幾千人既週年晚會，<br />\n差唔多絕大部份係新移民，<br />\n大多數都係大陸人上台拎奬金<br />\n嗰時我仲喺度諗保險業真係赤化得咁嚴重<im